attributionInfo.brokerName: Century 21 Hometown Realty, Arroyo Grande Office
Century 21 Hometown Realty, Paso Robles Office

data.description: Crisp 2 bedroom, 2 bath design on unusual lot formed by portions of 2 very deep lots fronting Pacific Ave. The result is a unique 55ft w X 80ft d lot. It is fully landscaped for low maintenance with a creative rock accented design for drainage. The floor plan has a bright great room with high ceilings, beam accents and lots of windows serving up peeks of the nearby ocean. A corner fireplace and wood-look flooring add a cozy feel. The kitchen also has peeks of the ocean, ample cabinet space and a host of quality appliances. There’s even an eat-at island, plus a breakfast area with view up Pacific Ave. Formal dining space behind the kitchen should easily seat 8 with room for a large china cabinet. The short hallway features solar tube lighting. Guest bath has shower over tub and single vanity. Guest bedroom is near. A generous primary suite has sliding door to the back yard offering a peek of the ocean and access to an EZ care yard and outdoor shower. Primary bath has double vanity and large shower. The laundry area is off the hall with sink, cabinets, counter, plus door to an oversized garage. Combined with the extra long driveway there is lots parking space on site. The location is near 2 Coastal Access Stairs making the opportunity even more attractive. Call your REALTOR® today.
